726401f-c.text:
Corona Avenue, north side, at Alstyne Avenue, showing the Card Farmhouse (1860). It was razed in 1925. The house stood in line of Alstyne Avenue, before the thoroughfare was extended to Corona
Avenue.
View 1: 1922
Views 2,3,4: 1923
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection
